{"word":"ἀγαστός","slug":"ἀγαστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀγαστός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀγατός</el> <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <a href='S:ἀγαστός'><el>ἀγαστός</el></a>, as <a href='S:θαυματός'><el>θαυματός</el></a> for <a href='S:θαυμαστός'><el>θαυμαστός</el></a>, <b>Hhymn.</b>; <a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:ἄγαμαι'><el>ἄγαμαι</el></a>\n<p/><i>deserving admiration</i>, later form of the <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b> <el>ἀγητός</el>, <i>admirable</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τῶς</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b> <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> for <el>ἀγαστός</el>, as <el>θαυματός</el> for <el>θαυμαστός</el>, <b>Hhymn.</b><p/>"}]}